ANS($answer->cmp);


Context()->texStrings;

SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR
$SOL
The focus is
\(\left(0, c\right)\) with
\(c=$c\) and the directrix is
\(y=-c\) with
\(c=$c\),  hence the equation of the parabola is
\[
y=\frac{1}{4c}{x}^{2}=\frac{{x}^{2}}{\{4*$c\}}.
\]
or
\[y-\frac{{x}^{2}}{\{4*$c\}}=0\]
END_SOLUTION

